Generate the components
To generate the boiler plate.

To install the application - npm install -g @angular/cli
To create a new template - ng new <name-of-app>
  Will ask for permission whether highly optimised code be created or not. - No
  Routing - Yes
  Styling. - CSS
  
  Now will make files automatically - like gitignore and all.
  
  ng serve - Serves the angular app. opens the app in the browser. Conver the browser compatiale code.
  
  


